title: STILL have not received my riot Kayle skin
body: Today it is October the 1st past the day 9/30 when they would give out the skins. I have not received the skin yet. I did get the summoner icon and Kayle but not the skin. Help!

replies.body:
We're currently handling these situations through a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), so I recommend reaching out there so we can take care of this for you.

Let me know if you have any questions.
